 stress 缓解压力","headword":"relieve stress"},{"type":"entry","text":"adjustment [əˈdʒʌstmənt]","headword":"adjustment"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.调整"},{"type":"entry","text":"reasonably [ˈriːznəbli]","headword":"reasonably"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad. 合理地"}]},{"number":1002,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"self-relief [ˌself rɪˈliːf]","headword":"self-relief"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.自我疏导"},{"type":"entry","text":"take a walk 散步","headword":"take a walk"},{"type":"entry","text":"duty [ˈdjuːti]","headword":"duty"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.责任"},{"type":"note","text":"◎sense of duty责任感"},{"type":"entry","text":"endeavour [ɪnˈdevə(r)]","headword":"endeavour"},{"type":"definition","text":"n./v.努力，尽力"},{"type":"note","text":"◎endeavour to do sth.努力做某事"},{"type":"entry","text":"confidence [ˈkɒnfɪdəns]","headword":"confidence"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.信心"},{"type":"note","text":"◎have confidence in对…有信心"},{"type":"entry","text":"mental preparation 心理准备","headword":"mental preparation"}]},{"number":1003,"blocks":[{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"},{"type":"example","text":"A：We were instructed to work overtime this evening. （我们接到指"},{"type":"text","text":"示今晚要加班。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Here it comes again.（又来了。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：You must endeavour to improve your skills.（你必须努力提高自"},{"type":"text","text":"己的能力。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：But I have been worn out when I get home every day. （可是每天"},{"type":"text","text":"回到家我都已经筋疲力尽了。）"}]}]}